summary: Compilation of my own personal retextures for the female forsworn outfit. There are currently 5, Wolf, Tigress, Snow Tigress, Snow Leopard, and Cow, but I will most likely be adding more.
descriptionHtml:
This is a Compilation of my own personal retextures for the female forsworn outfit. There are currently 5, Wolf, Tigress, Snow Tigress, Snow Leopard, and Cow, but I will most likely be adding more including but not limited to...

Leopard
Lion
White Lion
Bear (Cave, Mountain, Snow)
Fox
Goat

Once again, I did not alter the helmet for the outfit, because I believe that you could get a much better selection from [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5865]83Willow\'s mod[/url].

If you have any other suggestions feel free to put them down in the comments. Btw, I will not be doing any topless options, open an image editor and do it yourself please. I will do slightly skimpier options if they are wanted enough, but for now, this is what you get.

Also, I do not have the know how, time, or will to make these non-replacers and/or individual outfits, if anyone would be kind enough to do it feel free, just please respect the work I put into doing these by not reuploading the texture files anywhere.

One more thing, just for anyone that wants to know, I AM using CBBE armor meshes, but this will not affect the overall appearance of the texture on other armor meshes/bodies.
author: Tier1Dusty
